Module cathedral.game
Package de.fhkiel.ki.cathedral.game

Class Placement

java.lang.Object
de.fhkiel.ki.cathedral.game.Placement
public class Placement extends Object
The immutable class Placement is used to take a turn in a Game.

The Placement is composed by a Position, a Direction and a Building.
Since:
1.0

  • Constructor Summary

    Constructors
    Constructor
    Description
    Placement​(int x, int y, Direction direction, Building building)
    Instantiates a new Placement with x and y coordinates.
    The coordinates will be saved in a Position.
    The Direction is not legal in respect to the building, it will be transformed into a legal Direction.
